                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6452" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1643</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9977 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">和而不同：中国载人航天工程决策伦理问题探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Harmony Exists in Diversity: Exploration of Ethical Issues in China Manned Space Program Decision</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">欧阳桃花，唐伟，郑舒文，崔宏超，曾德麟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京航空航天大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国航天科技集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工程伦理；重大工程决策；中国载人航天；和而不同；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Engineering Ethics; Major Project Decision; China Manned Space Program; Harmony Exists in Diversity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">载人航天是规模庞大、系统复杂、关键技术多、可靠性和安全性要求极高、极具风险性的国家重大工程。自1992年立项以来，中国凭借“神舟”系列载人飞船、天宫系列空间站等型号任务，取得了举世瞩目的辉煌成就。然而中国追逐“飞天梦”的历程远不如所看到得这般一帆风顺，围绕载人航天工程“干不干”和“如何干”的决策过程，出现多次决策伦理冲突。载人航天工程为什么历经七年研讨论证，却迟迟难以上马？“机派”与“船派”的总体方案之争，“二舱”与“三舱”的技术路线之争，隐含着重大工程决策的哪些伦理困境？最终载人航天工程的破局之道又体现了哪些中国特色的伦理思想？能为重大工程的伦理决策带来哪些启示？本案例旨在引导学生学习重大工程决策的伦理思想，提高学生对工程伦理问题的分析和决策能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Manned space flight is a major national project with a large scale, complex system, multiple key technologies, high reliability and safety requirements as well as significant risk. Since its inception in 1992, China has made remarkable achievements with the Shenzhou manned spacecraft and Tiangong space station. However, China&#39;s pursuit of the ‘flying dream’ is not as smooth as it seems. There have been many ethical conflicts around the decision-making process of ‘whether to do it’ and ‘how to do it’. Why has it been so difficult to implement the manned space program after seven years of research and argumentation? What are the ethical dilemmas of major project decisions behind the disputes over the overall scheme between ‘space shuttle’and ‘manned spacecraft’ as well as the technical route between ‘two modules’ and ‘three modules’? What are the unique ethical thoughts of China in the way of the manned space program? What enlightenment can it bring to the ethical decision-making of major project? This case is designed to guide students to master the ethical awareness, ethical issues and ethical thoughts of China&#39;s major project decision. It is also hoped to improve students&#39; analysis of engineering ethics and decision-making ability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《工程伦理》、《商业伦理与社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工程伦理的概念；工程伦理问题识别；工程伦理背后的主要思想；伦理协同星；工程伦理困境化解步骤；“和而不同”的伦理思想</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
